\c 8
\s Kuputswa kweguta reAi
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Joshua: Usatya, kana kuvhunduswa; tora pamwe newe vanhu vese vehondo, zvino simukai mugokwira kuAi; ona ndapa muruoko rwako mambo weAi nevanhu vake neguta rake nenyika yake.
\v 2 Zvino uchaitira Ai sezvawakaitira Jeriko namambo waro; koga zvitapwa zvaro nemombe dzaro muchazvitorera kuva zvakajimbwa; uzviisire vavandiri muguta shure kwaro.
\p
\v 3 Naizvozvo Joshua wakasimuka nevanhu vese vehondo kuti vakwire kuAi; Joshua ndokusarudza varume zvuru makumi matatu mhare dzine simba, ndokuvatuma usiku.
\v 4 Zvino wakavaraira achiti: Tarirai, muchavandira guta shure kweguta; musaenda kure neguta, asi gadzirirai mese.
\v 5 Zvino ini nevanhu vese vanene tichaswedera kuguta. Zvino zvichaitika pavachatibudira sepakutanga kuti isu tichatiza pamberi pavo.
\v 6 Zvino vachabuda shure kwedu kusvika tavakweva vabve muguta; nokuti vachati: Vanotiza pamberi pedu sepakutanga. Naizvozvo tichatiza pamberi pavo;
\v 7 Zvino imwi muchasimuka kubva pakuvandira ndokutapa guta nokuti Jehovha Mwari wenyu acaripa muruoko rwenyu.
\v 8 Zvino kuchati kana matapa guta kuti mucharipisa nemoto, muchaita zvichienderana neshoko raJehovha; Onai ndinokurairai.
\p
\v 9 Zvino Joshua wakavatuma ivo ndokuenda pakuvandira, ndokugara pakati peBheteri neAi kumavirazuva eAi; asi Joshua wakarara pakati pevanhu usiku uhwo.
\v 10 Zvino Joshua wakamuka mangwanani-ngwanani ndokuverenga vanhu, ndokukwira iye nevakuru vaIsraeri, pamberi pevanhu vakaenda kuAi.
\v 11 Nevanhu vese vehondo vaakange anavo vakakwira ndokuswedera vakauya pamberi peguta, ndokudzika matende kumaodzanyemba eAi. Zvino kwaiva nemupata pakati pake neAi.
\v 12 Zvino wakatora varume vanenge zvuru zvishanu ndokuvavandirisa pakati peBheteri neAi kumavirazuva eguta.
\v 13 Zvino vakati vamisa, hondo yese yaiva kumaodzanyemba eguta, navavandiri vemavirazuva eguta, Joshua akaenda usiku uhwo pakati pemupata.
\v 14 Zvino zvakaitika mambo weAi paakazviona, kuti wakurumidza ndokumuka mangwanani-ngwanani, nevarume veguta vakabudira hondo naIsiraeri, iye nevanhu vake vese, nenguva yakatarwa, pamberi pebani, asi iye haana kuziva kuti kune vavandiri seri kweguta.
\v 15 Zvino Joshua naIsiraeri wese vakarohwa pamberi pavo, ndokutiza nenzira yerenje.
\v 16 Zvino vanhu vese vaiva muAi vakaunganidzwa kuteverera shure kwavo, zvino vakateverera shure kwaJoshua ndokukweverwa kure kubva muguta.
\v 17 Zvino hakuna kuva nemunhu wakasara muAi kana Bheteri asina kubuda kuteverera Isiraeri. Zvino vakasiya guta rakashama ndokuteverera Israeri.
\v 18 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Joshua: Tandavadzira bvumo riri muruoko rwako kuAi, nokuti ndaripa muruoko rwako. Joshua ndokutandavadzira bvumo raiva muruoko rwake kuguta.
\v 19 Zvino vavandiri vakasimuka nekukurumidza kubva panzvimbo dzavo, ndokumhanya paakangotandavadza ruoko rwake ndokupinda muguta, zvino vakaritapa, ndokukurumidza ndokupisa guta nemoto.
\v 20 Zvino varume veAi vakati vachicheuka, zvino onei utsi, zvino tarira, hweguta hweguta huchikwira kumatenga, zvino vakange vasina nzvimbo yavangatizira kuno kana uko; nevanhu vakange vatizira kurenje vakatendeukira mutevereri.
\v 21 Zvino Joshua naIsraeri wese vakati vaona kuti vavandiri vatapa guta, uye kuti utsi hweguta hwokwira, zvino vakadzoka ndokurova varume veAi.
\v 22 Neava vakabuda muguta kuzomirisana navo kusvika vava pakati paIsiraeri; vamwe kurutivi rwuno uye vamwe kune urwo; zvino vakavarova, zvino hakuna kusara munhu kwavari, wakasara kana wakapukunyuka.
\v 23 Zvino mambo weAi vaka\add mu\add*tora ari mupenyu ndokumuuisa kuna Joshua.
\v 24 Zvino zvakaitika Israeri apedza kuuraya vagari vese veAi musango murenje mavaivadzingirira, uye vese vawira pakupinza kwemunondo, kusvika vapedzwa, Israeri wese akadzokera kuAi, ndokurirova nemuromo wemunondo.
\v 25 Zvino zvakaitika kuti vese vakawa nezuva iro pavarume nepavakadzi, \add vaiva\add* zvuru gumi nezviviri, varume vese veAi.
\v 26 Nokuti Joshua haana kudzosa ruoko rwake, rwaakatandavadza narwo bvumo, kusvika aparadza chose vagari veAi.
\v 27 Koga mombe nezvingatapwa zveguta iro VaIsraeri vakazvitapira, zvichienderana nemuromo waJehovha waakaraira Joshua.
\v 28 Zvino Joshua wakapisa Ai, akariita murwi nekusingaperi, dongo kusvika nhasi.
\v 29 Akasungirira mambo weAi pamuti kusvikira madekwani; asi pakuvira kwezuva Joshua akavaraira, vakaturura chitunha chake pamuti, vakachikanda panopindwa napo pasuwo reguta, vakatutira pamusoro pacho murwi mukuru wamabwe; aripo kusvikira nhasi.
\p
\v 30 Zvino Joshua wakavakira Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri atari pagomo reEbhari,
\v 31 sezvakange zvarairwa vana vaIsraeri naMozisi, muranda waJehovha, sezvakanyorwa mubhuku yomurairo waMozisi; yakange iri aritari yamabwe asina kuvezwa; hakuna munhu wakange asimudzira dare pamusoro pawo; vakabayirapo Jehovha zvipiriso zvinopiswa, nokubayirawo zvipiriso zvokuyananisa.
\p
\v 32 Akanyorazve ipapo pamabwe murairo waMozisi, waakanyora pamberi paVaIsraeri.
\v 33 VaIsraeri vese navakuru vavo navatariri vavo, navatongi vavo vakamira paareka nechouno necheseri, pamberi pavapristi VaRevhi, vaisitakura areka yesungano yaJehovha, pamwe chete navatorwa navakange vaberekerwa munyika; hafu yavo pamberi pegomo reGerizimi, nehafu yavo pamberi pegomo reEbhari; sezvakange zvarairwa naMozisi, muranda waJehovha, kuti vatange kuropafadza vana vaIsraeri.
\v 34 Pashure akarava mashoko ese omurayiro, okuropafadza nookutuka, sezvazvakanyorwa zvese mubhuku yomurayiro.
\v 35 Kwakange kusine shoko rimwe, pazvese zvakange zvarairwa naMozisi, risina kurahwa naJoshua pamberi peungano yese yaVaIsraeri, navakadzi navana, navatorwa vakange vagere pakati pavo.
